  <scopecontent audience="internal" id="aspace_f65e17e981fb3ea6f84c1b04b6e1b727">
    <head>Content Description</head>
<p>Programs, flyers, posters, and playbills associated with the production of Baldwin's plays; a complete set of bookstore promotional materials by Dial Press advertising the publication of The Fire Next Time and reissue of his backlist, and two recordings on vinyl. Also included are ephemera related to Baldwin's participation in the Civil Rights Movement.</p>  </scopecontent>
  <odd audience="internal" id="aspace_a8afffa4a92d1b12a047494bc928027c">
    <head>General</head>
<p>Forms part of the George Bixby Collection of James Baldwin featuring ca 270 published books and contributions to periodicals.</p>  </odd>
